node.text:
Two infamous tricks at two different spots. Which trick is your favourite? 🤔

@raphaelcastilhoalves 360 Flip over the bump to trash can or @brunosenrabp Hardflip Backside 180 over the bump to bar? 

Let us know your vote in the comments. Watch more from the new episode of #MundoGustavo taking over #Barcelona. Link in bio for the full trip. 

#skate #360flip #hardflip #skatetrip

node.text:
💥 Sometimes spots look so good in footage but there is usually something wrong that you can only see when you skate it - a crack, sketchy run up, security or in this case a pole to dodge after the landing! 

 @brunosenrabp unfortunately went straight into it after this perfectly caught Backside Flip. 

Watch more from our newest episode of Mundo Gustavo. Link in bio. 📺
#skate #skateboarding #hallofmeat #redbullskate #mundogustavo

📍#Barcelona is a heaven for skateboarders filled with perfect spots all around the city, a fun party scene, the beach to recover & skaters from around the world!

Hit the link in our bio to join @gustavoribeiro & @gabriel_p_ribeiro as they show you around the city. 
 
#skate #spain #MundoGustavo #skatetrip

node.text:
There is a reason why every skater wants to hit #Barcelona. @gustavoribeiro & the @ementasb crew will show you how they did it. This city never gets old!

Dropping tonight 12pm California / 8pm Portugal. More info in our stories! 👀

#skate #MundoGustavo #spain #skatetrip
